{/* CHARTS SECTION */}
<Container sx={{ py: 6 }}>
  <Typography
    variant="h4"
    textAlign="center"
    fontWeight="bold"
    gutterBottom
  >
    ðŸ“Š Exam Trends
  </Typography>

  <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center">
    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
      <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
        <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom textAlign="left">
            Exam Distribution
          </Typography>
          <Pie data={pieData} />
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </Grid>

    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
      <Card sx={{ height: '100%' }}>
        <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom textAlign="left">
            Monthly Registrations
          </Typography>
          <Bar data={barData} />
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </Grid>
  </Grid>
</Container>
